<div class="content-panel content">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-12 medium-8 large-8 columns">
    
    <h3>Are you a blogger dedicated to telling your travel stories? Or an explorer with an eye for photography? Maybe you prefer to experience the world from behind the lens of a video camera? </h3><br>
    <h3>If we’ve just described you to a T, you could become a TID Travel Scout!</h3>
      
    <hr> 
    <h3>What’s a TID Travel Scout?</h3>
    <p>TID is recruiting customers who are frequent globetrotters and want to share their experiences with other TID travellers. As our official storytellers, TID Travel Scouts will have their content published regularly on TID’s website and social pages. </p>

    
    <hr>
    <h3>What’s in it for you?</h3>
    <p>In return for your submissions, you will receive an Annual Multi-trip policy to fuel your travel passion. That’s 12 months’ worth of travel insurance which covers you, your gear and your trips as you travel throughout the year.</p>
    
    <p>To sweeten the deal, you’ll also get an iPad mini 2 32GB with Wi-Fi (RRP $429) so you can post, tweet and ‘gram on the go.</p>
     
