    <hr>
    <h3>Who can apply?</h3>

    <p>To be considered, you’ll need to -</p>
    
      <ol>
        <li>Be a TID customer</li>
        <li>Be an amateur travel blogger, video maker or photographer</li>
        <li>Have your own blog, YouTube/Vimeo, Flickr, Instagram and/or Pinterest accounts</li>
        <li>Travel overseas at least 3 times in the 12 month period of your AMT policy</li>
        <li>Be an Australian resident and agree to the T&amp;Cs of our travel insurance policy</li>
        <li>Agree to provide a minimum of 10 pieces of content in your chosen medium over the 12 month period of your AMT policy</li>
        <li>Be a passionate traveller who fits into one of these four themes:
        </li>
      </ol>  
     
      <ul class="small-block-grid-1 medium-block-grid-2 large-block-grid-4 travel-scout-themes">
        <li>
          <h5>Fun</h5>
          <img src="/Media/Default/campaigns/travel-scout/travel-scout-fun.jpg">
          Whether you are at Disneyland, skiing in Niseko or diving in the Maldives, this theme is for active travellers who are always on the hunt for adventure.</li>
        <li>
          <h5>Family</h5>
          <img src="/Media/Default/campaigns/travel-scout/travel-scout-family.jpg">
          You may be celebrating an anniversary, visiting family or getting away for the school holidays.  This theme puts family at the centre of your travels.</li>
        <li>
          <h5>Food</h5>
          <img src="/Media/Default/campaigns/travel-scout/travel-scout-food.jpg">
          If you plan your trips around food then this is the one for you.  Booking a Michelin star restaurant months ahead or seeking out the best of the local cuisine is what you’re about.</li>
        <li>
          <h5>Film</h5>
          <img src="/Media/Default/campaigns/travel-scout/travel-scout-film.jpg">
          After seeing ‘The Secret Life of Walter Mitty’ you are packing your Nikon and heading to Iceland.  You are inspired by the cinematography of film and TV (plus you may just want to snap a selfie with a star).</li>
      </ul>  
